[micromark][] factory to parse labels (found in media, definitions).

## Contents

*   [What is this?](#what-is-this)
*   [When should I use this?](#when-should-i-use-this)
*   [Install](#install)
*   [Use](#use)
*   [API](#api)
    *   [`factoryLabel(â€¦)`](#factorylabel)
